data.description: Classic mid century Mossman home nestled near Uptown! Many recent improvements including newer hot water heater, updates to both baths, newer electric stove top, dishwasher, new AC unit, new furnace and new LPV flooring.  Lovely hardwood floors throughout, except the large family room addition, which includes a 4th bedroom (or home office). There are skylights in the kitchen, baths. The one car garage has a professionally designed workbench for the handy person. Beautiful Quigley Park is only a block and half away ideal for kids and pets, good schools, and the convenience of proximity to uptown shopping and dining. Come check out this rare find and make it yours!
